reg_info.full_title: O. Reg. 38/01: DEADLINE FOR TORONTO UNDER SECTION 447.66
reg_info.act_under: Municipal Act   Loi sur les municipalités

content.content: 1. April 30, 2001 is prescribed as the later deadline for 2001 for the City of Toronto, for the purposes of section 447.66 of the Act. O. Reg. 38/01, s. 1.
content.raw_html: 1. April 30, 2001 is prescribed as the later deadline for 2001 for the City of Toronto, for the purposes of section 447.66 of the Act. O. Reg. 38/01, s. 1.
